Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.60,0:00:19.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- MINAMI, I--\N- WHAT DO YOU WANT?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- UH, I'M...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.19,0:00:23.94,Main,,0,0,0,,SORRY ABOUT EARLIER.\N- WHATEVER.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:26.32,Main,,0,0,0,,SHOULDN'T YOU BE MAKING OUT\NWITH MIZUKI OR SOMETHING?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:27.82,Main,,0,0,0,,- UH, NO.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:29.07,Main,,0,0,0,,WE SHOULD BE THINKING\NOF ANOTHER STRATEGY.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.15,0:00:31.45,Main,,0,0,0,,I MEAN, IF WE LOSE\NAGAINST CLASS B,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.53,0:00:33.49,Main,,0,0,0,,HIMEJI MIGHT HAVE TO\NCHANGE SCHOOLS.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:35.24,Main,,0,0,0,,THEN WE'D BE STUCK\NTRYING TO REPLACE HER.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:37.04,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT ARE YOU\NTRYING TO SAY, JERK?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.12,0:00:38.45,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:40.62,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHY IS IT ALWAYS ABOUT\NMIZUKI WITH YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.71,0:00:42.83,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY DOES SHE GET TO BE\NTHE ONLY ONE WHO MATTERS?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.92,0:00:43.84,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHE'S NOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.92,0:00:44.96,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, YOU COULD\NHAVE FOOLED ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:46.63,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY DON'T YOU CARE\NABOUT MY FEELINGS?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:48.13,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU TREAT ME LIKE I'M A GUY.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:50.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT?\NIT'S NOT LIKE THAT, I SWEAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.22,0:00:52.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- IF THEY TRY TO MAKE HER MOVE,\NI'LL TALK TO MIZUKI'S PARENTS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.13,0:00:53.89,Main,,0,0,0,,AND YOU CAN BE\NTOGETHER FOREVER.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.97,0:00:55.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- MINAMI--
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.14,0:00:56.81,Main,,0,0,0,,- JUST STAY OUT OF MY\NLIFE, ALL RIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:00:59.10,Main,,0,0,0,,I DON'T EVER WANT\NTO SEE YOU AGAIN.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:01.56,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( theme music playing )
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.64,0:01:04.56,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( singing in Japanese )
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.82,0:02:32.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara: AND NOW TO\NRECAP THE LAST EPISODE.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.32,0:02:34.07,Main,,0,0,0,,WHOO-HOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.15,0:02:36.24,Main,,0,0,0,,NEMOTO KYOUJI,\NTHE CLASS B REP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.32,0:02:39.07,Main,,0,0,0,,WAS PLANNING TO DECLARE\NWAR ON CLASS F.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.16,0:02:40.99,Main,,0,0,0,,HE FIGURED THEIR\NFIGHTING POWER WAS LOW
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:43.25,Main,,0,0,0,,SINCE THEY JUST FINISHED\NTHEIR SUSPENSION.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:46.50,Main,,0,0,0,,AKIHISA AND FRIENDS\NTHEN DECIDED TO PROVOKE CLASS D,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:49.04,Main,,0,0,0,,HOPING THEY WOULD\NDECLARE WAR FIRST.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:51.00,Main,,0,0,0,,FIGHTING CLASS D\NWOULD GIVE THEM TIME
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.09,0:02:53.92,Main,,0,0,0,,TO TAKE THEIR RECOVERY TEST\NAND REBUILD THEIR STRENGTH.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.01,0:02:56.84,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY FIGURED CLASS B\NWOULD BE LESS LIKELY TO STRIKE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.93,0:02:59.30,Main,,0,0,0,,IF CLASS F HAD A LITTLE MORE\NFUEL IN THEIR TANK, SO TO SPEAK.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:03.02,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji: TO GET D'S ATTENTION,\NWE DECIDED AKIHISA AND MINAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.10,0:03:04.64,Main,,0,0,0,,SHOULD PRETEND\NTO BE DATING.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.73,0:03:06.23,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT WOULD REALLY\NPISS OFF MIHARU
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.31,0:03:08.44,Main,,0,0,0,,AND IT WOULD BE ON.\NBUT NOW THAT WHOLE PLAN IS SHOT,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.52,0:03:10.27,Main,,0,0,0,,SO HERE WE ARE.\N- ( chuckles )
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.36,0:03:11.61,Main,,0,0,0,,- MAN, YOU'RE SUCH A TROLL.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.69,0:03:13.44,Main,,0,0,0,,I CAN'T BELIEVE\NYOU SCREWED THIS UP.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.53,0:03:15.07,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT THE HELL\NWERE YOU THINKING?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.15,0:03:16.70,Main,,0,0,0,,HOW DOES ANY OF THAT\NDRAMATIC CRAP HELP
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.78,0:03:17.78,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT WE'RE TRYING\NTO DO, MAN?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.86,0:03:19.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- SORRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.28,0:03:20.95,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DEFINITELY THINK\NMORE ACTING LESSONS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:22.70,Main,,0,0,0,,WERE REQUIRED HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:25.29,Main,,0,0,0,,I THOUGHT SHIMADA AND HIMEJI\NWERE VERY BELIEVABLE THOUGH.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.37,0:03:28.46,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, WOW.\NTHANK YOU SO MUCH.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHY DON'T YOU CARE\NABOUT MY FEELINGS?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:33.80,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU TREAT ME\NLIKE I'M A GUY.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.88,0:03:35.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY, KOUTA.\NWHAT ARE THINGS LOOKING LIKE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.30,Main,,0,0,0,,OVER THERE IN CLASS B?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.38,0:03:39.30,Main,,0,0,0,,- THEY'RE CURRENTLY ABOUT\N70% RECOVERED,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.39,0:03:41.39,Main,,0,0,0,,AND IT ACTUALLY LOOKS LIKE\NSOME OF THEM ARE ALREADY
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.47,0:03:42.97,Main,,0,0,0,,GETTING READY FOR\NTHE NEXT WAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:44.39,Main,,0,0,0,,- THEN THEY'RE MOVING\NFASTER THAN I THOUGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.47,0:03:45.89,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT'S KIND OF SCARY.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.97,0:03:47.31,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY'RE REALLY ON A MISSION.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.39,0:03:49.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE HAVE TO FIGURE OUT\NHOW TO STALL THEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.40,0:03:50.98,Main,,0,0,0,,SO GET READY, KOUTA.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.06,0:03:53.15,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M GONNA NEED YOU TO\NSTART A RUMOR IN CLASS B.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.23,0:03:54.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- HIT ME WITH IT.\N- TELL THEM CLASS D
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:58.49,Main,,0,0,0,,IS PREPPING FOR AN ST WAR,\NAND CLASS B IS THEIR TARGET.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:04:00.07,Main,,0,0,0,,- WORD.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:02.07,Main,,0,0,0,,- DO YOU REALLY THINK\NTHAT'S GONNA WORK?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.16,0:04:03.99,Main,,0,0,0,,- THE ONLY THING NEMOTO\NREALLY CARES ABOUT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:05.50,Main,,0,0,0,,IS GETTING BACK ON TOP.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.25,Main,,0,0,0,,THE DUDE WANTS TO WIN,\NPERIOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.33,0:04:09.33,Main,,0,0,0,,HE'LL TRY TO AVOID\NFIGHTING A SERIES OF WARS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.42,0:04:11.50,Main,,0,0,0,,TO KEEP HIS CLASS\NFROM GETTING EXHAUSTED.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.58,0:04:13.67,Main,,0,0,0,,IF HE FINDS OUT CLASS D\NIS AFTER THEM HARDCORE,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.75,0:04:15.59,Main,,0,0,0,,HE'LL LAY OFF OF US\NFOR AWHILE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:17.17,Main,,0,0,0,,- MAKES SENSE.\NIT'S NOT LIKE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.26,0:04:19.76,Main,,0,0,0,,CLASS F'S EQUIPMENT IS\NA PRIZE FOR ANYONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.84,0:04:21.68,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO HIDEYOSHI, YOU'RE UP.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.76,0:04:24.51,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S NOW YOUR DROP TO DRAW\NMIHARU SHIMIZU OUT OF CLASS D.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.60,0:04:26.10,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU'LL BE THE ONE\NTO HANG ON MINAMI
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.10,Main,,0,0,0,,AND MAKE LEZZI-TRON\NWANT TO ATTACK US.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:29.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( grunts )
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.02,0:04:31.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- AS SOON AS THEY STRIKE,\NWE'RE HOME FREE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:32.81,Main,,0,0,0,,SO BRUSH UP, BRO.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.90,0:04:34.44,Main,,0,0,0,,- BUT WHY DO I\NHAVE TO DO IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.52,0:04:36.11,Main,,0,0,0,,- THANKS FOR GIVING ME\NTHE OPPORTUNITY TO GO OVER
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.19,0:04:38.36,Main,,0,0,0,,HOW AKIHISA RUINED\NOUR ENTIRE LIVES AGAIN
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.44,0:04:40.78,Main,,0,0,0,,AND HOW WE CAN'T USE HIM OR\NHIMEJI FOR THIS TASK ANYMORE.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.57,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, YEAH.  I'M ON IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.66,0:04:44.83,Main,,0,0,0,,- ARE YOU HUNGRY?\N- WHO, ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.91,0:04:46.79,Main,,0,0,0,,- YES, YOU.\NARE YOU HUNGRY?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.75,Main,,0,0,0,,- NOW THAT YOU MENTION IT,\NI COULD GO FOR A SANDWICH.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.83,0:04:51.37,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT IS NEVER\NGOOD NEWS, MY FRIEND.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:53.38,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU ARE THE CORNERSTONE\NOF THIS OPERATION,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.46,0:04:55.05,Main,,0,0,0,,AND WE NEED TO FILL YOU UP\NWITH SOMETHING GOOD
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:56.34,Main,,0,0,0,,SO YOU'LL BE\NREADY TO FIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.63,Main,,0,0,0,,ISN'T THAT RIGHT, HIMEJI?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.71,0:04:59.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT?\NYEA, I MEAN...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:01.22,Main,,0,0,0,,IF HE'S HUNGRY,\NHE WON'T BE ABLE TO FOCUS
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:04.35,Main,,0,0,0,,ON GETTING THE JOB DONE.\N- ( groans )
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.43,0:05:05.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO THAT'S ON YOU THEN.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.81,0:05:07.22,Main,,0,0,0,,FIND SOMETHING TO\NSTUFF HIS FACE WITH.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:09.27,Main,,0,0,0,,- I FORGOT.\NI HAD LUNCH ALREADY,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.35,0:05:10.35,Main,,0,0,0,,AND I'M PRETTY STUFFED.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:11.73,Main,,0,0,0,,I COULDN'T SWALLOW\NANOTHER MOUTHFUL.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- IS THAT THE LUNCH\NYOU'RE TALKING ABOUT, HUH?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:15.81,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S DELICIOUS.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.90,0:05:17.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- AAH!\NHOW COULD YOU DO THAT TO ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.07,0:05:19.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU WERE ASKING FOR IT, MAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:22.32,Main,,0,0,0,,SO, HIMEJI, YOU THINK YOU COULD\NMAKE SOMETHING FOR AKIHISA?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.40,0:05:23.91,Main,,0,0,0,,- SURE, I'D BE DELIGHTED TO.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.99,0:05:25.74,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY.\NWHAT ARE YOU TRYING TO DO?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.82,0:05:28.08,Main,,0,0,0,,- FEED YOU. NOW WHAT DO\NYOU FEEL LIKE EATING?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.75,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T KNOW.\N( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.83,0:05:32.71,Main,,0,0,0,,IF I PICK SOMETHING HEALTHY,\NI JUST MIGHT SURVIVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:34.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE DON'T HAVE ALL DAY,\NYOU KNOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.42,0:05:37.25,Main,,0,0,0,,- OKAY, THERE HAVE TO BE\NAS FEW INGREDIENTS AS POSSIBLE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:39.25,Main,,0,0,0,,SO THERE'S LESS CHANCE\NSHE'LL POISON ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.34,0:05:40.92,Main,,0,0,0,,I CHOOSE BOILED EGGS.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.01,0:05:43.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- SOUNDS PERFECT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:45.85,Main,,0,0,0,,AKIHISA WOULD LIKE YOU\NTO MAKE HIM SOME JELLO.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:47.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T EVEN KNOW\NWHAT'S IN THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.51,0:05:49.10,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT IF IT SLOWS ME DOWN?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.52,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE HAVE TO MAKE SURE\NYOU EAT DURING THE OPERATION.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.60,0:05:52.19,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( grunts )\N- MAKE SURE TO PUT IT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:54.10,Main,,0,0,0,,IN ALUMINUM POUCHES\NSO HE CAN CARRY THEM WITH HIM.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:55.77,Main,,0,0,0,,- I WON'T EVEN BE ABLE TO SEE\NWHAT COLOR IT IS IN THERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:57.61,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'LL DO IT.\NI WON'T LET YOU DOWN!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.69,0:05:59.27,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAIT!  CAN YOU AT LEAST\NTELL ME WHAT KIND YOU'RE MAKING,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.36,0:06:00.94,Main,,0,0,0,,SO I'LL HAVE SOME IDEA?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:02.78,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE GONNA\NHAVE TO KNOCK IT OFF.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.78,Main,,0,0,0,,LOOK, CALM DOWN. NOBODY'S\NREALLY GONNA MAKE YOU EAT THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.86,0:06:06.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- HUH?\N- I NEEDED HER TO HELP US
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:07.87,Main,,0,0,0,,MAKE SOME MORE WEAPONS,\NTHAT'S ALL.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.45,Main,,0,0,0,,( chuckles )\N- OH.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.54,0:06:11.79,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY DIDN'T YOU SAY SO\NIN THE FIRST PLACE?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.87,0:06:13.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- BECAUSE NOW SHE'S\NGONNA TRY TO FEED IT TO YOU,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.79,0:06:15.00,Main,,0,0,0,,AND THAT'S GONNA BE\NFREAKING HYSTERICAL.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.08,0:06:17.84,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE A COLD-HEARTED SNAKE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.92,0:06:20.05,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( giggles )
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.13,0:06:22.13,Main,,0,0,0,,FIRST THING ON THE LIST\NIS TO GET THE GELATIN
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:24.72,Main,,0,0,0,,AND SUGAR NICE AND READY.\N- NOT BAD.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:26.47,Main,,0,0,0,,SHE LOOKS LIKE SHE KNOWS\NWHAT SHE'S DOING.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:28.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, THAT'S GOOD.\N- NOW TO MIX THE COCOA POWDER
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.30,0:06:31.06,Main,,0,0,0,,IN WITH THE CORN POTAGE\NLIKE CHOCOLATE COVERED POPCORN.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.14,0:06:33.48,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHOA.  WHERE DID SHE\NGET THAT RECIPE FROM?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.56,0:06:34.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHH, SHUT UP.\NSHE'LL HEAR YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.06,0:06:36.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- WILL IT BE THE ORANGE\NOR THE SCALLION?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:40.23,Main,,0,0,0,,THEY'RE BOTH SO GOOD,\NI CAN'T DECIDE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.32,0:06:43.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- SERIOUSLY? YOU SHOULDN'T HAVE\NTO THINK ABOUT THAT ONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.36,0:06:45.07,Main,,0,0,0,,- KNOCK IT OFF, YO.\NSHE'S TRYING TO PICK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:46.57,Main,,0,0,0,,INGREDIENTS THAT ARE\NTHE MOST NUTRITIOUS,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.66,0:06:47.70,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU UNGRATEFUL TURD.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:49.41,Main,,0,0,0,,- SCALLIONS ARE MUCH HEALTHIER,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.49,0:06:51.33,Main,,0,0,0,,ESPECIALLY WITH NATTO.\N- MAKE IT STOP.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:53.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAIT A MINUTE, I THINK I\NREMEMBER READING SOMETHING
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.66,0:06:55.92,Main,,0,0,0,,ABOUT NATTO THAT SAYS IT'S NOT\NAS GOOD FOR OUR BLOOD FLOW
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:57.92,Main,,0,0,0,,AS WE ONCE THOUGHT.\N- SAFE.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.00,0:07:00.17,Main,,0,0,0,,- BUT IT'S STILL AN\NEXCELLENT SOURCE OF PROTEIN.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.25,0:07:01.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( groans )
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:02.92,Main,,0,0,0,,- THERE WE GO.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:04.67,Main,,0,0,0,,AND I JUST REMEMBERED\NIT'S BLUE FISH SKIN
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.76,0:07:06.34,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT IMPROVES BLOOD FLOW.\N( giggles )
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.43,0:07:08.35,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S A DOUBLE PLAY.\N- THAT'S A FISH.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.43,0:07:10.76,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY IS SHE PUTTING A\NFISH IN JELLO? THAT'S GROSS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.85,0:07:12.85,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHE KNOWS HOW HARD\NIT IS FOR YOU TO BE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.77,Main,,0,0,0,,SUCH AN IDIOT, SO SHE'S TRYING\NTO FEED YOUR BRAIN.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.85,0:07:17.19,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S SWEET, REALLY.\N- HE'LL LOVE THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.27,0:07:19.36,Main,,0,0,0,,OH MY GOSH,\NTHIS ISN'T GOING TO TASTE GOOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.44,0:07:21.36,Main,,0,0,0,,- I KNEW YOU'D\NCOME THROUGH, HIMEJI.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.44,0:07:23.53,Main,,0,0,0,,- EVERYONE KNOWS YOU'RE SUPPOSED\NTO ADD MUSTARD TO NATTO.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.61,0:07:25.19,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT'S NOT GOING TO FIX IT!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:27.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- AND MAYBE A LITTLE\NGINGER FOR THE FISH.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:28.49,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE JUST\NMAKING IT WORSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.57,0:07:30.37,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT OTHER SECRET\NINGREDIENTS CAN I ADD?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:32.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- SECRETS DO NOT\NMAKE GOOD FOOD.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.33,0:07:34.37,Main,,0,0,0,,- I KNOW!\NI BET SOME HOT SAUCE
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.45,0:07:36.16,Main,,0,0,0,,WILL MAKE IT EXCITING.\N- LET'S GO.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.25,0:07:37.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( crying )
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU HEAR ANYMORE,\NYOU WON'T EAT IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:40.04,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DIDN'T GET TO SEE\NHOW HOT THE HOT SAUCE WAS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.13,0:07:42.55,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT IF I CAN'T TAKE IT?\NI'M AFRAID OF HEAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:44.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara:\NNOT THAT IT REALLY MATTERS.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.80,0:07:47.18,Main,,0,0,0,,- I HOPE YOU GUYS LIKE IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.97,Main,,0,0,0,,I MADE A MESS OF\NTHE HOME EC ROOM.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.05,0:07:50.80,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M GONNA GO\NCLEAN IT UP.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.89,0:07:52.56,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT ARE WE SUPPOSED\NTO DO WITH THESE?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.64,0:07:54.47,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL, I THINK NEMOTO\NIS SENDING A MESSENGER
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.56,0:07:55.89,Main,,0,0,0,,OVER TO CLASS D.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.98,0:07:57.56,Main,,0,0,0,,HIS MISSION WILL BE\NTO FIND OUT
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:07:58.98,Main,,0,0,0,,IF THEY'RE ACTUALLY\NSTARTING A WAR LIKE WE SAID.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.06,0:08:00.40,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, GREAT.\NNOW WHAT ARE WE GONNA DO?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:01.90,Main,,0,0,0,,AS SOON AS HE GETS THERE,\NHE'LL SEE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.82,Main,,0,0,0,,WE MADE THE WHOLE THING UP.\N- VERY SIMPLE.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:05.44,Main,,0,0,0,,WE HAVE TO ASSASSINATE\NTHE MESSENGER.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.53,0:08:06.99,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasping )\N- WE MAKE IT LOOK LIKE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.07,0:08:08.74,Main,,0,0,0,,SOMEONE FROM CLASS D DID IT,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.82,0:08:11.16,Main,,0,0,0,,LIKE A DECLARATION OF WAR\NBEFORE THE FIGHTING STARTS.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.24,0:08:13.16,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHEN HE FINDS OUT\NONE OF HIS MEN IS DOWN,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.24,0:08:15.91,Main,,0,0,0,,HE WON'T QUESTION WHO DID IT.\N- I DON'T KNOW. IT SOUNDS CRUEL.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.00,0:08:17.75,Main,,0,0,0,,- BATTLES ARE CRUEL,\NMY FRIEND.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:19.17,Main,,0,0,0,,KOUTA, IT'S TIME\NTO GET MOVING.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.25,0:08:20.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- INDEED, IT IS.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.84,0:08:32.64,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT THE HECK'S THAT?\N- ( students gasp )
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.68,0:08:40.52,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( grunts )\NWHO'S THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.31,Main,,0,0,0,,( gagging )
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.40,0:08:45.19,Main,,0,0,0,,- REST IN PIECE.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:50.07,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasping )
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.54,0:08:57.91,Main,,0,0,0,,MOMMY.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:09:00.12,Main,,0,0,0,,- MISSION ACCOMPLISHED.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:01.88,Main,,0,0,0,,- PERFECTION AS USUAL.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.96,0:09:03.54,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT WAS SERIOUSLY IMPRESSIVE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.63,0:09:05.04,Main,,0,0,0,,- SOME ARE JUST\NBORN WITH IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.13,0:09:06.88,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT WAS A NICE\NLITTLE WARM-UP THOUGH.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:09.30,Main,,0,0,0,,- HOW WERE YOU ABLE TO DO THAT\NWITHOUT ANYONE NOTICING?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.38,0:09:11.47,Main,,0,0,0,,- Kouta: YOU'RE ASKING\NTOO MANY QUESTIONS.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.55,0:09:13.64,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT'S IMPORTANT HERE\NIS THAT NOW NEMOTO SEES THIS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.64,Main,,0,0,0,,AS A WARNING CASUALTY\NFROM CLASS D.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:17.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- GOOD.\NNOW WE HAVE TIME TO PREPARE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.60,0:09:20.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEP.  SO HOW HAVE\NNEGOTIATIONS BEEN GOING?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.18,0:09:22.64,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE AGREED TO MEET IN ONE OF\NTHE EMPTY CLASSROOMS.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:24.27,Main,,0,0,0,,MINAMI SAID SHE WOULD\NBE THERE AS WELL.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.36,0:09:25.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- AND THAT'S WHERE\NTHE MAGIC HAPPENS.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:27.23,Main,,0,0,0,,WE'VE GOT THIS THING\NIN THE BAG.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.32,0:09:28.49,Main,,0,0,0,,- HOW DO WE KNOW FOR SURE
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.57,0:09:30.24,Main,,0,0,0,,THOSE GUYS ARE GONNA\NRESPOND TO THAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.32,0:09:32.07,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, I'VE GOT IT\NALL WORKED OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.15,0:09:33.78,Main,,0,0,0,,JUST LEAVE IT TO ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:35.99,Main,,0,0,0,,- THERE IS STILL ONE THING\NTHAT KIND OF WORRIES ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.08,0:09:37.41,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT IS IT?\NDID SOMETHING HAPPEN?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:39.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- I SAW NEMOTO EARLIER.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:42.25,Main,,0,0,0,,HE WAS TALKING VERY INTENSELY\NTO SOMEONE IN CLASS A.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:44.67,Main,,0,0,0,,- CLASS A, HUH?\NTHAT'S VERY STRANGE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.75,0:09:47.04,Main,,0,0,0,,I WONDER WHAT IT WAS ABOUT.\N- THERE YOU ARE.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:50.67,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasps ) SHOUKO.\NWHAT-- WHAT DO YOU WANT?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.76,0:09:53.34,Main,,0,0,0,,- I CAN'T BELIEVE THIS.\NWHY ARE YOU STILL AT SCHOOL?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.43,0:09:54.93,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHY WOULDN'T I\NBE AT SCHOOL?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:56.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M SO SORRY.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.51,0:09:58.51,Main,,0,0,0,,I JUST HEARD THAT\NYOUR MOM COLLAPSED TODAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.60,0:10:01.68,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO WAY.\NARE YOU POSITIVE IT WAS MY MOM?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.77,0:10:03.81,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU'RE MAKING THAT UP. THE\NWOMAN'S NEVER EVEN HAD A COLD.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.89,0:10:05.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHE NEEDS YOU.\NLET'S GO CHECK ON HER.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.06,0:10:07.36,Main,,0,0,0,,I CAN'T GO ANYWHERE RIGHT NOW.\NI'M IN THE MIDDLE OF
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.44,0:10:08.94,Main,,0,0,0,,SOMETHING VERY IMPORTANT.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.02,0:10:10.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- THIS IS YOUR MOTHER\NWE'RE TALKING ABOUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.03,0:10:13.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- SHE'S FINE. I'LL CHECK\NON HER WHEN I GET DONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:14.61,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE DONE NOW.\N- LET ME GO.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.70,0:10:15.95,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT'S WRONG WITH YOU?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.03,0:10:19.28,Main,,0,0,0,,- SOMETHING'S FISHY HERE,\NAND IT'S NOT FISH.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.37,0:10:20.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT DO YOU MEAN?\NIS HE OKAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.95,0:10:22.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T KNOW.\NWHY WOULDN'T YUUJI BE
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.96,0:10:24.96,Main,,0,0,0,,THE FIRST ONE THEY CONTACTED\NABOUT HIS MOTHER?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:26.96,Main,,0,0,0,,- MAYBE BECAUSE\NTHEY COULDN'T REACH HIM?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.21,Main,,0,0,0,,HE SAID HE HAD TO TAKE\NHIS PHONE IN FOR REPAIRS.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:31.59,Main,,0,0,0,,- THEN THEY COULD HAVE\NJUST USED THE P.A. SYSTEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.67,0:10:33.97,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO THAT MEANS THAT NEMOTO\NWAS PROBABLY TALKING TO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:35.55,Main,,0,0,0,,SOMEONE IN CLASS A\NABOUT ALL THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.63,0:10:37.39,Main,,0,0,0,,- HE KNEW YUUJI\NWOULD GO WITH SHOUKO.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.56,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT EVIL SON OF A--\N- THIS SUCKS.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.64,0:10:41.68,Main,,0,0,0,,IF I UNDERSTOOD RIGHT,\NOUR NEXT STEP IN THE OPERATION
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.52,Main,,0,0,0,,WAS TO PISS OFF MIHARU\NSO SHE'D ATTACK YUUJI.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:45.27,Main,,0,0,0,,- NEVER HEARD\NANYTHING ABOUT THIS?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:46.19,Main,,0,0,0,,- NOT A PEEP.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:47.73,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT IS NEMOTO\NTRYING TO DO?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.81,0:10:50.15,Main,,0,0,0,,DO YOU THINK HE MAY HAVE\NFIGURED OUT OUR STRATEGY?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:53.49,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO, BUT HE'S PROBABLY TRYING\NTO BUY SOME TIME AS WELL.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:55.32,Main,,0,0,0,,- I BET HE'S TRYING\NTO KEEP US AT BAY
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.40,0:10:57.32,Main,,0,0,0,,UNTIL HE FIGURES OUT EXACTLY\NWHAT CLASS D IS PLANNING.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.24,0:11:00.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- WELL PLAYED, NEMOTO.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.95,0:11:02.79,Main,,0,0,0,,- BETTER LATE THAN NEVER,\NRIGHT?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.87,0:11:05.16,Main,,0,0,0,,- MINAMI, HI.\N- ( scoffs )
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.25,0:11:06.67,Main,,0,0,0,,I ONLY CAME HERE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.75,0:11:08.46,Main,,0,0,0,,BECAUSE I KNOW YOU CAN'T\NDO THIS WITHOUT ME, OKAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.54,0:11:11.34,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO WHAT'S OUR\NPLAN OF ACTION NOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.42,0:11:12.84,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, I GUESS\NWE HAVE TO DO SOMETHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:15.76,Main,,0,0,0,,YUUJI ISN'T HERE,\NSO WE HAVE NO CHOICE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.84,0:11:17.97,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT TO HANDLE THIS\NON OUR OWN.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.68,0:11:24.02,Main,,0,0,0,,- Miharu: BAKA AND TEST!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.86,0:11:34.78,Main,,0,0,0,,- SWEET SUGAR DUMPLING!\NI'M SO HAPPY TO SEE YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:36.20,Main,,0,0,0,,HUG ME!\N- NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:38.11,Main,,0,0,0,,LET GO, MIHARU.\NYOU'RE CHOKING ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.20,0:11:39.37,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, LAMBKIN,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.45,0:11:40.70,Main,,0,0,0,,YOUR SWEET BREASTICLES\NREMIND ME OF THE OCEAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:42.20,Main,,0,0,0,,SO SMOOTH AND PERFECT!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:43.95,Main,,0,0,0,,- MAYBE YOU'RE\NTHINKING OF THE HORIZON
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:45.46,Main,,0,0,0,,WHICH IS FLAT\NAND LEADS TO NOWHERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.54,0:11:47.46,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE STILL TOUCHING ME.\NI SAID GET OFF.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.54,0:11:49.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU SHOULD KNOW THAT\NI THINK OF YOU EVERY MINUTE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.79,0:11:51.50,Main,,0,0,0,,360 DAYS A YEAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.59,0:11:53.30,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO YOU MUST TAKE\NTHE HOLIDAYS OFF,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.38,0:11:54.88,Main,,0,0,0,,GOOD FOR YOU.\N- ENOUGH OF THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.96,0:11:56.72,Main,,0,0,0,,MINAMI IS AKIHISA'S GIRLFRIEND.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:58.80,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT THEY HAVE IS LIKE\NBEAUTIFUL AND STUFF.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.88,0:12:00.55,Main,,0,0,0,,I WON'T LET YOU\NCOME BETWEEN THEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:02.47,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAY TO GO.\NJUST AS WE PLANNED.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.55,0:12:04.60,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT SORT OF INSANITY\NARE YOU SPITTING AT ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.68,0:12:06.81,Main,,0,0,0,,ARE YOU TRYING TO TELL ME\NTHAT MY GUMDROP PRINCESS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:09.06,Main,,0,0,0,,WANTS ANYTHING TO DO\NWITH THAT MOLDY MUFFIN WRAP?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.14,0:12:11.36,Main,,0,0,0,,LOOK AT THAT FACE. IS THAT A\NFACE THAT LOVES TROLL BOYS?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:12.98,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT MAKES AN\NAPE FART LIKE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.07,0:12:14.73,Main,,0,0,0,,THINK YOU'RE WORTHY OF\NTHE GINGERSNAP GODDESS?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.82,0:12:17.32,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO.  YOU'RE RIGHT.\NI'M NOT EXACTLY A STUD.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:19.78,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M PRETTY SCRAWNY,\NAND I'M NOT SMART, BUT--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:22.08,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T CARE.\NTHAT DOESN'T MATTER.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.16,0:12:23.91,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS GOES WAY BEYOND\NLOOKS OR SKILLS,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:25.41,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU SHALLOW ASS.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.50,0:12:29.25,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS IS MUCH MORE COMPLICATED.\N- ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.33,0:12:32.67,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'VE HAD MY EYE ON YOU\NFOR A LONG TIME NOW,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.75,0:12:34.84,Main,,0,0,0,,AND THE WAY YOU TREAT PEOPLE\NYOU SUPPOSEDLY CARE ABOUT
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.92,0:12:36.01,Main,,0,0,0,,IS DISGUSTING.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:37.67,Main,,0,0,0,,MY PRINCESS IS IN\NTHE SAME CLASS AS
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.76,0:12:39.93,Main,,0,0,0,,BOTH YOU AND HIMEJI,\NBUT FOR SOME REASON
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:42.01,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU TREAT THEM BOTH\NVERY DIFFERENTLY.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:44.76,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU ARE AS SWEET\NAS CANDIED APPLES
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:47.93,Main,,0,0,0,,WHEN IT COMES TO HIMEJI. TREAT\NHER LIKE SHE'S THE PRINCESS.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.02,0:12:49.60,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT WHEN IT COMES TO MY LOVE,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:51.86,Main,,0,0,0,,NOT ONLY ARE YOU RUDE\NAND INCONSIDERATE,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:54.90,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT IT'S LIKE YOU FORGET\NSHE'S A GIRL ALTOGETHER.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.98,0:12:57.69,Main,,0,0,0,,ARE YOU THAT STUPID?\NDO YOU NOT SEE THE CHARM
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.78,0:13:00.28,Main,,0,0,0,,AND DELICACY THAT OOZES\NFROM HER EVERY PORE?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.36,0:13:02.78,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT KIND OF PIG-BRAINED IDIOT\NTREATS SOMEONE LIKE HER
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.87,0:13:04.53,Main,,0,0,0,,AS JUST ONE OF THE GUYS?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:06.87,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS IS NOT JUST AN ASSESSMENT\NOF YOUR MISERABLE LOOKS
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:10.00,Main,,0,0,0,,OR YOUR EMBARRASSING\NSUGGESTION OF ACADEMIC SKILLS.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.08,0:13:12.88,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU MAKE ME SICK.\NTHIS IS ABOUT A BLACK SOUL
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:15.04,Main,,0,0,0,,WHO WOULD THROW THE HEART OF\NA PERFECT ANGEL IN THE TRASH
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:17.25,Main,,0,0,0,,JUST TO PURSUE SOMEONE\NAS AVERAGE AS HIMEJI.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.34,0:13:18.67,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S PATHETIC. YOU\NTHINK MINAMI'S A GUY?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.76,0:13:22.01,Main,,0,0,0,,MAN, YOU REALLY MUST BE\NDUMBER THAN YOU LOOK, AKIHISA.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.09,0:13:24.35,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( crying )
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.43,0:13:25.93,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasping )\N- MINAMI!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.01,0:13:28.56,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT HAPPENS WHEN\NYOU CATCH UP TO HER?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.64,0:13:30.56,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU GONNA WRESTLE WITH HER\NAND CALL HER NAMES
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.64,0:13:32.85,Main,,0,0,0,,UNTIL YOU BOTH LAUGH\NAND THEN SPIT SHAKE ON IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:37.15,Main,,0,0,0,,YEAH, WHY DON'T YOU GO REMIND\NHER WHY SHE SHOULD HATE YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.23,0:13:39.40,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'LL GO TALK TO HER.\NMIHARU'S RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:41.74,Main,,0,0,0,,WE DON'T WANT TO MAKE THINGS\NANY WORSE RIGHT NOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.82,0:13:44.32,Main,,0,0,0,,- UH, I DON'T KNOW\NWHAT'S GOING ON IN HERE,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.41,0:13:46.74,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I'M PRETTY SURE\NI'M NOT NEEDED.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.21,Main,,0,0,0,,- DID YOU REALLY COME TO SHOVE\NYOUR SORRY EXCUSE FOR LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.29,0:13:55.13,Main,,0,0,0,,IN MY FACE?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.21,0:13:56.71,Main,,0,0,0,,'CAUSE I'LL TELL\NYOU RIGHT NOW,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.25,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU ARE NOT WORTHY TO\NCOMPETE WITH ME
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.34,0:14:00.22,Main,,0,0,0,,FOR ANYONE'S HEART.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:02.34,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU NEED TO PROVE SOMETHING,\NOBVIOUSLY.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.42,0:14:05.10,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT LOVE IS NOT ABOUT WHO WANTS\NTO FIGHT FOR WHAT YOU HAVE,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.18,0:14:07.43,Main,,0,0,0,,AND EVEN IF IT WAS,\NI'M THE ONLY ONE WHO GETS
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.51,0:14:09.77,Main,,0,0,0,,HOW HARD YOU HAVE TO FIGHT\NFOR SOMEONE LIKE HER.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:11.64,Main,,0,0,0,,SO I'VE ALREADY WON.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.73,0:14:13.52,Main,,0,0,0,,- MIHARU, WAIT.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.60,0:14:16.19,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T HAVE ANYTHING\NMORE I WANT TO SAY TO YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.27,0:14:17.77,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO, YOU'VE SAID IT ALL.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.86,0:14:19.19,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT THERE'S SOMETHING\NI NEED TO TELL YOU,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:21.36,Main,,0,0,0,,NO MATTER WHAT HAPPENS.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:37.34,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE, THE SECOND YEAR\NSTUDENTS OF CLASS D
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.42,0:14:39.38,Main,,0,0,0,,HEREBY DECLARE WAR\NON CLASS F!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:40.96,Main,,0,0,0,,- All: WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.05,0:14:42.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T GET IT.\NWHAT'S HAPPENING NOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.88,0:14:45.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- I THOUGHT YOU GUYS SAID\NIT DIDN'T GO AS PLANNED.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.30,0:14:51.39,Main,,0,0,0,,- WE WEREN'T EXPECTING A WAR.\NNOW WHAT?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.47,0:14:53.93,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S GONNA BE TOUGH FIGHTING\NWITH THIS LOW LEVEL OF STRENGTH.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:14:55.64,Main,,0,0,0,,- DON'T WORRY.\NIT'S PART OF OUR PLAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:57.48,Main,,0,0,0,,- YUUJI.\N- JUST AS WE THOUGHT,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:59.32,Main,,0,0,0,,IT WAS A BUNCH OF\NSTRATEGIC B.S.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.40,0:15:01.28,Main,,0,0,0,,MY MOM'S FINE\NAND HEALTHY AS A DONKEY.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.36,0:15:03.15,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU MEAN HORSE,\NBUT THAT'S AWESOME.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:05.49,Main,,0,0,0,,- WAY TO STEP IT UP,\NAKI, MY MAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.57,0:15:07.32,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT DIDN'T GO EXACTLY\NAS WE PLANNED,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.41,0:15:08.99,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT YOU STILL MANAGED\NTO HIT THE TARGET
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:11.58,Main,,0,0,0,,AND UNLEASH THE CHICK BEAST.\N- NOW WE'RE AT WAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:13.37,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I DON'T KNOW HOW WE'LL\NBE ABLE TO FIGHT THEM ALL.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:14.83,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S TRUE.\NWE'LL NEVER SURVIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:17.33,Main,,0,0,0,,IN AN ALL OUT BATTLE.\NWHICH MEANS...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.42,0:15:19.63,Main,,0,0,0,,WE'LL HAVE TO FIGHT\NREPRESENTATIVES ONE-ON-ONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.89,Main,,0,0,0,,- I HAVE TO SAY, I'M IMPRESSED\NYOU DIDN'T RUN AWAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:31.01,Main,,0,0,0,,- MY THOUGHTS EXACTLY.\N- BELIEVE ME,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.10,0:15:33.60,Main,,0,0,0,,THE LAST THING I WANT TO DO\NIS BATTLE MY LOVE SQUIRREL,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.68,0:15:35.60,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT IF IT MEANS A CHANCE\NAT MAKING JERK JERKY
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.68,0:15:37.31,Main,,0,0,0,,OUT OF THIS PIG,\NIT'S WORTH IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.39,0:15:39.02,Main,,0,0,0,,- I GUESS WE'LL\NSEE ABOUT THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.11,0:15:41.82,Main,,0,0,0,,OKAY, IT'S ALL YOU\NFROM HERE ON OUT, BUDDY.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.90,0:15:45.20,Main,,0,0,0,,MAKE ME PROUD, SON.\N- I AM ALL OVER THIS ONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.28,0:15:47.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE GONNA PAY\NFOR WHAT YOU'VE DONE.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.28,0:15:48.62,Main,,0,0,0,,I HOPE YOU'RE READY, DORK.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.24,Main,,0,0,0,,MAY WE HAVE PERMISSION?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.33,0:15:51.78,Main,,0,0,0,,- I APPROVE!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.29,0:15:54.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'VE BEEN WAITING FOR THIS.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:56.75,Main,,0,0,0,,- READY AND...\N- Both: SUMMON!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:59.54,Main,,0,0,0,,- BEFORE WE BEGIN, I HAVE A\NQUESTION I WANT TO ASK YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.63,0:16:01.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT'S THAT?\N- WHAT YOU SAID EARLIER.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:03.71,Main,,0,0,0,,DID YOU MAKE ALL THAT UP\NJUST SO YOU COULD START
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:06.84,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS WAR WITH CLASS D?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:09.22,Main,,0,0,0,,RIGHT.\NI SHOULD HAVE KNOWN.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.51,0:16:14.06,Main,,0,0,0,,- BEFORE WE LEFT,\NI SAW HER TEAR UP.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.14,0:16:16.89,Main,,0,0,0,,I KNEW IT WAS BECAUSE\NTHE THINGS I SAID TOUCHED HER.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.98,0:16:20.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I UNDERSTOOD HER PAIN.\NPAIN YOU CAUSED HER!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:23.69,Main,,0,0,0,,SHE SHOULD NEVER EVEN HAVE\NTO KNOW THOSE FEELINGS EXIST!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.77,0:16:26.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- HOW ARE YOU ALLOWED\NTO BE IN HER PRESENCE?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.74,0:16:28.90,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU SHOULD BE\NCHAINED AND LOCKED UP.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.99,0:16:31.32,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU COULDN'T BE TRUSTED TO\NHOLD A CONVERSATION WITH HER
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.41,0:16:33.91,Main,,0,0,0,,WITHOUT MANIPULATING AND\NTHEN DISMISSING HER FEELINGS.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:36.25,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S NOT FAIR!\NIT'S NOT FAIR!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.33,0:16:37.75,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU LIED TO HER.\NYOU USED HER.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.83,0:16:39.42,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU ONLY PRETENDED\NTO BE HER FRIEND
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:41.42,Main,,0,0,0,,SO THAT YOU COULD\NKEEP HER AROUND FOR BATTLES!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.50,0:16:42.84,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU DON'T GIVE\NA CRAP ABOUT HER!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.92,0:16:46.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( shouts )\N- ( grunts )
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.80,0:16:50.63,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE WRONG.\NI WAS TELLING THE TRUTH!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.72,0:16:52.14,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( screams )
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:54.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M NOT THE SMARTEST\NGUY IN THE WORLD,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.18,0:16:57.10,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT I KNOW THERE ARE SOME\NTHINGS YOU NEVER JOKE ABOUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.18,0:16:59.52,Main,,0,0,0,,EVER.\NI WAS TELLING THE TRUTH!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.60,0:17:01.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHY SHOULD I BELIEVE\NA WORD YOU SAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.02,0:17:03.52,Main,,0,0,0,,- THEY WEREN'T JUST WORDS.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.61,0:17:05.57,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT I SAID WAS\NEXACTLY HOW I FEEL!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:07.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( screams )
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.11,0:17:08.94,Main,,0,0,0,,( grunts )
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.03,0:17:10.78,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M NOT FALLING FOR IT\NA SECOND TIME.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.95,0:17:17.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- THAT'S ENOUGH.\N- ( both gasp )
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:25.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT THE CRAP?\NWHAT ARE YOU DOING?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.21,0:17:26.84,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU CAN GO NOW.\NWE'LL TAKE IT FROM HERE ON OUT.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:29.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE KIDDING.\NTHIS IS FOUL PLAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:30.26,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU CAN'T DO THAT!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.34,0:17:31.72,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU CAN CALL IT\NWHATEVER YOU WANT.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:33.97,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS ISN'T SOME KIND OF GAME.\NTHIS IS WAR.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.05,0:17:36.64,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S WAR!\N- NO!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.72,0:17:38.06,Main,,0,0,0,,- GO GET 'EM, BOYS.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.14,0:17:41.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( moans, shouts )
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.39,0:17:43.48,Main,,0,0,0,,- STOP IT!  TRAITORS!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.86,0:17:50.82,Main,,0,0,0,,OW!\N( whimpering )
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.90,0:17:53.07,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY?!  WHY ARE THEY\NATTACKING ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.16,0:17:54.99,Main,,0,0,0,,( yelping )
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.08,0:17:57.16,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS IS THE WORST PAIN\NI'VE EVER FELT.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.24,0:18:00.91,Main,,0,0,0,,IT'S LIKE A MILLION SHARP BLADES\NSHOOTING IN AND OUT OF MY BODY.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:03.08,Main,,0,0,0,,- MIHARU.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.17,0:18:05.59,Main,,0,0,0,,SO WHAT DO YOU THINK? I'M\NPRETTY SURE THAT KIND OF PAIN
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.67,0:18:07.00,Main,,0,0,0,,WILL LAST AWHILE.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:08.59,Main,,0,0,0,,I KNOW HE DESERVES\NMUCH MORE THAN THIS,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:10.17,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT IS IT POSSIBLE THAT YOU\NCAN FORGIVE HIM FOR NOW?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:12.59,Main,,0,0,0,,- MAYBE FOR NOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:14.89,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS ISN'T SOMETHING I'M GOING\NTO GET OVER VERY QUICKLY.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.97,0:18:17.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( shouts )\N- PROMISE ME THIS PUNK-ASAURUS
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.18,0:18:18.85,Main,,0,0,0,,WILL BE CONFINED TO\NTHE REMEDIAL CLASSROOM,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.93,0:18:20.27,Main,,0,0,0,,AND I'LL GRANT\NTHE CEASE-FIRE.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:21.68,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'VE GOT TO BE KIDDING.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.77,0:18:23.60,Main,,0,0,0,,WAS THIS PART OF YOUR PLAN,\NDOUCHER?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:25.15,Main,,0,0,0,,- OF COURSE.\NSORRY ABOUT THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:27.52,Main,,0,0,0,,I KNEW THERE WAS NO WAY\NWE COULD WIN AGAINST CLASS D
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:29.03,Main,,0,0,0,,IN OUR CURRENT STATE.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:30.86,Main,,0,0,0,,SO I JUST FIGURED\NNEGOTIATING A CEASE-FIRE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.94,0:18:32.78,Main,,0,0,0,,WAS THE BEST THING TO DO.\N- IT DOESN'T MATTER.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:34.36,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU STILL HURT\NMY LOVE KITTEN,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.45,0:18:36.20,Main,,0,0,0,,AND THAT PART HASN'T CHANGED.\N- ( groans )
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:39.83,Main,,0,0,0,,AND I'M SO SORRY FOR THAT,\NFROM THE BOTTOM OF MY-- GAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.91,0:18:41.87,Main,,0,0,0,,- I'M ONLY LETTING YOU\NOFF THE HOOK THIS EASILY
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:44.00,Main,,0,0,0,,BECAUSE I BELIEVE SOME OF THE\NTHINGS YOU TOLD ME WERE TRUE.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.08,0:18:48.04,Main,,0,0,0,,- AAH!\N- ( screams )
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.13,0:18:50.55,Main,,0,0,0,,- SO JUST IMAGINE WHAT YOU'D\NBE GETTING IF YOU HAD LIED.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:52.55,Main,,0,0,0,,- AND THAT'S WHAT I CALL\NA SWEET DEAL.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:53.97,Main,,0,0,0,,ALL RIGHT, GUYS,\NLET'S HEAD BACK.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.05,0:18:55.43,Main,,0,0,0,,GOOD JOB.\N- All: YEAH!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.72,0:18:59.56,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( stammers )
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.64,0:19:01.97,Main,,0,0,0,,( whimpers )\NHUH?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:03.39,Main,,0,0,0,,AHH.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.48,0:19:05.06,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S SO GREAT\NTO HAVE YOU BACK.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:07.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara: WITH THAT,\NTHE WAR WAS FINALLY OVER.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.73,0:19:09.73,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT'S THE SCOOP, KOUTA?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.82,0:19:12.65,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT LOOKS LIKE NEMOTO\NAND CLASS B FINALLY GAVE UP.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.74,0:19:14.24,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEP.\NJUST AS WE PREDICTED.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:16.07,Main,,0,0,0,,- GOOD.\NI STILL CAN'T SEE
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:18.07,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT THEY WOULD HAVE\NGOTTEN OUT OF IT ANYWAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:20.66,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, YEAH. I PICKED THIS\NTHING UP LIKE YOU ASKED.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:22.49,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT ARE YOU\NUSING THAT FOR?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.58,0:19:23.95,Main,,0,0,0,,- Miharu: DID YOU REALLY\NCOME TO SHOVE YOUR SORRY
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.04,0:19:25.58,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT?\N- EXCUSE FOR LOVE IN MY FACE?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:27.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO, PLEASE TELL ME YOU DIDN'T.\N- I MAY OR MAY NOT
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:29.42,Main,,0,0,0,,HAVE RECORDED THAT\NENTIRE CONFERENCE.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:30.75,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO, WHAT IS IT REALLY?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:32.55,Main,,0,0,0,,IS IT SOME KIND OF NEAT NEW\NAUDIOBOOK YOU FOUND?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.63,0:19:34.84,Main,,0,0,0,,- KEEP SQUEEZING.  HE'S STILL\NGOT ENOUGH AIR TO TALK.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.92,0:19:37.47,Main,,0,0,0,,- STOP SQUIRMING LIKE THAT.\N- LET ME GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.55,0:19:38.93,Main,,0,0,0,,- I GOT YOU NOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:40.22,Main,,0,0,0,,AND SORRY, I AM NOT\NLETTING YOU GO.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.31,0:19:43.10,Main,,0,0,0,,- TURN IT OFF!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.18,0:19:45.14,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU'RE BEING TOO LOUD.\NI CAN'T HEAR ANYTHING.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.23,0:19:48.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- Miharu: I DON'T HAVE ANYTHING\NMORE I WANT TO SAY TO YOU.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:50.73,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( muffled shouts )
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.82,0:19:53.57,Main,,0,0,0,,THINGS AREN'T ALWAYS\NEXACTLY THE WAY THEY SEEM.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:56.03,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, I KNOW YOU'RE NOT\NREALLY DATING MY BUTTERCUP.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.11,0:19:58.70,Main,,0,0,0,,THAT WAS PAINFULLY OBVIOUS.\N- 'KAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:20:02.29,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT THAT'S NOT WHAT I MEAN.\NUHH...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.37,0:20:04.12,Main,,0,0,0,,I PROMISE YOU,\NYOU'RE NOT THE ONLY ONE
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:06.21,Main,,0,0,0,,WHO RECOGNIZES\NHOW AMAZING MINAMI IS.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:08.12,Main,,0,0,0,,- I CAN'T BELIEVE\NYOU'RE STILL TRYING!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.21,0:20:10.29,Main,,0,0,0,,DO YOU NOT GET THAT I SAW YOU\NSAY AWFUL THINGS TO HER?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:11.71,Main,,0,0,0,,I SAW YOU TREAT HER\NLIKE A GUY,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.80,0:20:13.34,Main,,0,0,0,,AND I SAW HER CRYING\NBECAUSE OF IT.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:15.21,Main,,0,0,0,,- OKAY, LISTEN.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.30,0:20:17.88,Main,,0,0,0,,I DON'T TREAT HER LIKE\NA PRINCESS, YOU'RE RIGHT.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.97,0:20:19.89,Main,,0,0,0,,AND I'M PROBABLY ACTING\NTHE SAME WAY AROUND HER
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:22.68,Main,,0,0,0,,AS I WOULD MY GUY FRIENDS\NWITH THE WAY I JOKE AND STUFF.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:26.14,Main,,0,0,0,,BUT THAT'S BECAUSE...\N- BECAUSE WHY?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.23,0:20:28.14,Main,,0,0,0,,BE CAREFUL.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.23,0:20:30.31,Main,,0,0,0,,- BECAUSE I DON'T HAVE TO.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:32.98,Main,,0,0,0,,MINAMI IS SOMEONE I CAN\NJUST BE MYSELF AROUND.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.07,0:20:34.98,Main,,0,0,0,,I DON'T HAVE TO PUT ON\NAN ACT FOR HER.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.07,0:20:36.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I LOVE HANGING OUT WITH HER
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:38.57,Main,,0,0,0,,BECAUSE WE JUST GET\NEACH OTHER'S WEIRDNESS.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.65,0:20:40.28,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU CAN'T KID AROUND\NWITH MOST GIRLS LIKE THAT.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:43.28,Main,,0,0,0,,AND IT'S THE DUDE PART\NTHAT MAKES HER SO HOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:47.50,Main,,0,0,0,,( gasps )\N- WHOA.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:48.75,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU JUST SAID SHE WAS HOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.83,0:20:51.00,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH, I HEARD IT TOO,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:54.00,Main,,0,0,0,,AND I DON'T DISAGREE, BUT I'M\NSURPRISED YOU SAID IT OUT LOUD.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.09,0:20:56.71,Main,,0,0,0,,- ME TOO.  SO ROMANTIC.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:59.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHY?  WHY IS THIS\NHAPPENING TO ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.51,0:21:01.64,Main,,0,0,0,,WHY DID THEY OUT OF ALL PEOPLE\NHAVE TO HEAR IT?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:03.01,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T KNOW.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:04.93,Main,,0,0,0,,SOMETHING ABOUT THAT WAS\NJUST SO SWEET AND BEAUTIFUL.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.02,0:21:07.35,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU SAID THE DUDE PARTS\NMADE HER HOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.43,0:21:08.89,Main,,0,0,0,,MY HEART IS BEATING SO FAST.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.98,0:21:11.35,Main,,0,0,0,,- YOU {\i1}CAN{\i0} BE YOURSELF\NAROUND HER.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:12.94,Main,,0,0,0,,- Akihisa:\NSOMEONE KILL ME, PLEASE.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:15.03,Main,,0,0,0,,THIS SUCKS.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:16.98,Main,,0,0,0,,- NO, DON'T STRETCH MY ARMS.\N( giggles )
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.07,0:21:19.53,Main,,0,0,0,,SIS!  OH MY GOSH,\NYOU'RE HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.24,Main,,0,0,0,,I MISSED YOU!\N- HI.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:22.57,Main,,0,0,0,,I MISSED YOU TOO.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.66,0:21:24.20,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, NO.\NWHAT'S THE MATTER?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.28,0:21:25.87,Main,,0,0,0,,YOUR FACE LOOKS LIKE\NYOU'VE BEEN CRYING.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.95,0:21:27.62,Main,,0,0,0,,- I JUST--\NI DON'T KNOW WHAT TO DO.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.70,0:21:29.29,Main,,0,0,0,,- OH, NO, TEARS!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.37,0:21:31.79,Main,,0,0,0,,DID SOMEBODY CALL YOU\NA NAME AT SCHOOL?  TELL ME.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:34.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- IT'S NOT THAT.\NIT'S JUST--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.21,0:21:35.80,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT HAPPENED?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.88,0:21:38.38,Main,,0,0,0,,- THE WORST THING THAT\NCOULD HAVE POSSIBLY HAPPENED.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:40.05,Main,,0,0,0,,I'VE FALLEN\NIN LOVE WITH SOMEONE,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:43.01,Main,,0,0,0,,AND I DON'T KNOW\NIF HE LOVES ME BACK.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.09,0:21:46.22,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( theme music playing )
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.31,0:21:47.43,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( singing in Japanese )
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.98,0:23:17.40,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( sighs )\NI HATE TODAY SO MUCH.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.48,0:23:22.15,Main,,0,0,0,,HOW AM I SUPPOSED TO APOLOGIZE\NTO MINAMI FOR WHAT I SAID?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.23,0:23:23.82,Main,,0,0,0,,- HEY.\N- ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.90,0:23:25.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- WHAT'S THE MATTER\NWITH YOU TODAY?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.99,0:23:27.95,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU LOOK LIKE CRAP, AKI.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.03,0:23:30.79,Main,,0,0,0,,- ( gasps )
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.87,0:23:32.49,Main,,0,0,0,,MINAMI...\N- THAT'S MY NAME.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.58,0:23:36.33,Main,,0,0,0,,- YEAH.  UH... IT IS.\NI'M SORRY ABOUT YESTERDAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.42,0:23:38.13,Main,,0,0,0,,- I DON'T KNOW WHAT\NYOU'RE TALKING ABOUT,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.21,0:23:39.96,Main,,0,0,0,,SO YOU JUST TOLD ON YOURSELF.\NWHAT LIES ARE YOU SPREADING?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.05,0:23:41.76,Main,,0,0,0,,- NOTHING!\NTHAT'S NOT WHAT I MEAN.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.84,0:23:43.51,Main,,0,0,0,,- GOOD.  BECAUSE NEXT TIME\NYOU PULL A STUNT LIKE THAT,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:45.22,Main,,0,0,0,,I'M NOT LETTING YOU OFF\NWITHOUT A PUNCH.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.30,0:23:48.55,Main,,0,0,0,,- HUH?\N- ( giggles )
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.64,0:23:51.31,Main,,0,0,0,,YOU IDIOT.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.39,0:23:54.35,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara:\NQUESTION NUMBER 11.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.43,0:23:55.93,Main,,0,0,0,,WHAT DO YOU CALL SOMEONE\NYOU WERE CLOSE TO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.02,0:23:57.52,Main,,0,0,0,,WHEN YOU WERE SMALL?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.60,0:24:00.36,Main,,0,0,0,,- Yuuji:\NA CHILDHOOD FR-- ( gagging )
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.44,0:24:01.90,Main,,0,0,0,,- Shouko: A FIANCEE.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.98,0:24:03.82,Main,,0,0,0,,- Akihisa: NEXT TIME, YUUJI,\NSHOUKO, AND CHILDHOOD MEMORIES.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.90,0:24:05.82,Main,,0,0,0,,- Fukuhara:\NTHIS WILL BE ON THE TEST.
